{
  "stem": "13469.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And and that was a treat for us to go on the tram and be treated to some of these restaurants and, in particular, have very nice ice creams and things like that kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So that's some of the things that we remember.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We didn't have a car or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We had bicycles.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we moved around by tram in Holland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "However, all these happy events changed on the 10th of May, 1940.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I mean, these are some-- when, when people ask me, you know, what do you remember more than-- one day that I always remember is the 10th of May, 1940.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Because that was the day when the Germans invaded Holland--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--and Belgium and France.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- I remember quite a lot about that particular day, kind of thing, in particular, that we could hear all the planes overhead.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we could see the parachutes coming down out of the sky.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think that's something that we, or that I, will always remember.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as schoolboys, of course, we were all watching kind of thing with interest.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't realize the implications of it, I don't suppose.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But all the school kids together, we all used to go and, and stand there and watch all the parachuters coming down.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there were roadblocks set up all over Holland, apparently.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But there were some near, near us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we went-- we all went to this roadblock.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because what, what we hadn't realized-- we'd only recently find out-- is that there was a big Fifth Column in Holland.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Many Germans had infiltrated into Holland before the invasion, before the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they were all coming out of the woodwork on the 10th of May, when the Germans invaded, as saboteurs, to sabotage behind the lines.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
